text: Richard Edward Doran (born December 26, 1956) is an American lawyer and politician. He was the 34th Florida Attorney General from November 5, 2002, to January 3, 2003. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Florida attorneys general Category:Living people Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from Ohio Category:Lawyers from Ohio
